class_notes: Students must have access to TikTok, IG Reel or be willing to use a recording device to upload dance videos to Canvas.  Students must also create a Flipgrid account using their full Emory email.  We have periodic ZOOM Q & A meetings throughout the semester.
course_description: A basic health course using a variety of physical activities to experience and practice the principles of fitness related to cardiovascular conditioning, muscular strength and resistance, and plyometric training.
